entry.value: select * from lakehouse.etladmin.etl_job WHERE src_table IN ('AHN_PHUCTHAM_QUYETDINH')

SELECT LISTAGG( COLUMN_NAME ,',') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY COLUMN_NAME ASC) LIST_COL_INS_TAR, LISTAGG( COLUMN_NAME || '= S.' || COLUMN_NAME ,',') LIST_COL_UPD, LISTAGG( 'S.' || COLUMN_NAME ,',') WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY 'S.' ||COLUMN_NAME ASC) LIST_COL_INS_SRC FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS WHERE upper(TABLE_SCHEMA) =upper( 'LAKEHOUSE.${integration_schema}') AND upper(TABLE_NAME) = upper('${integration_table}')
update lakehouse.etladmin.etl_job set max_scn= ${new_max_src_scn} where src_table = '${src_table}' and src_schema= '${src_schema}'
select a.*, ora_rowscn OP_NO, TRUNC(SYSDATE) AS LOAD_DATE, SYSTIMESTAMP AS LOAD_TIME from ${src_schema}.${src_table} a where ora_rowscn > ${max_scn} and ora_rowscn <= ${new_max_src_scn}
select NVL(max(ora_rowscn),0) src_scn from ${src_schema}.${src_table} a where ora_rowscn > ${max_scn}
